============================================================
CONFIG REQUIREMENTS
============================================================

Update root `.env.example`:

FEDERATION_ENABLED=true
FEDERATION_MODE=advisory
FEDERATION_FAIL_CLOSED=true
FEDERATION_MEMBERSHIP_APPROVAL_REQUIRED=true
FEDERATION_TRUST_EXCHANGE_ENABLED=true
FEDERATION_TRUST_EXCHANGE_DRY_RUN=true

TRUST_NETWORK_ENABLED=true
TRUST_REGISTRY_ENABLED=true
TRUST_SCORE_ENABLED=true
TRUST_SCORE_MIN_CONFIDENCE=0.60
REPUTATION_TRACKING_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_PASSPORT_ENABLED=true
COMPLIANCE_PASSPORT_SUMMARY_ONLY=true

VERIFIABLE_OS_ENABLED=true
ATTESTATION_ENABLED=true
ATTESTATION_SIGNING_PROVIDER=mock
ATTESTATION_SIGNING_DRY_RUN=true
ATTESTATION_REQUIRE_EVIDENCE=true
ATTESTATION_EXCLUDE_SECRETS=true

EVIDENCE_BUNDLE_ENABLED=true
EVIDENCE_BUNDLE_SUMMARY_ONLY=true
EVIDENCE_BUNDLE_REQUIRE_DLP=true

PROVENANCE_LEDGER_ENABLED=true
PROVENANCE_LEDGER_MODE=hash_chain
PROVENANCE_LEDGER_DRY_RUN=true
PROVENANCE_RETENTION_DAYS=365

RELEASE_ATTESTATION_ENABLED=true
SBOM_ATTESTATION_ENABLED=true
POLICY_ATTESTATION_ENABLED=true
AUDIT_EXPORT_VERIFIABLE_ENABLED=true

AI_PROVENANCE_ENABLED=true
PROMPT_PROVENANCE_ENABLED=true
MODEL_PROVENANCE_ENABLED=true
EVAL_PROVENANCE_ENABLED=true
DECISION_PROVENANCE_ENABLED=true
AI_LINEAGE_ENABLED=true

FEDERATED_MARKETPLACE_GOVERNANCE_ENABLED=true
FEDERATED_MARKETPLACE_FAIL_CLOSED=true

Rules:
- Federation must be advisory by default.
- Federation trust exchange must be dry-run by default.
- Trust exchange requires explicit approval.
- Compliance passports are summary-only by default.
- Evidence bundles must exclude secrets.
- DLP must run before evidence bundles and attestations.
- Signing provider is mock/dry-run by default.
- Provenance ledger is hash-chain shell by default, not a real blockchain.
- No raw private keys, signing keys, API keys, or secrets may be persisted.
- Federated marketplace governance must fail closed when safety state is unknown.

