============================================================
API RESPONSE FORMAT
============================================================

All endpoints must use standard response shape:

Success:

{
  "ok": true,
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Error:

{
  "ok": false,
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human readable message"
  },
  "timestamp": "ISO_DATE"
}

Required error codes:

- FEDERATION_DISABLED
- FEDERATION_NOT_FOUND
- FEDERATION_MEMBER_NOT_FOUND
- FEDERATION_MEMBERSHIP_APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- TRUST_BOUNDARY_BLOCKED
- FEDERATION_POLICY_BLOCKED
- REGIONAL_TRUST_EXCHANGE_BLOCKED
- TRUST_NETWORK_DISABLED
- TRUST_ENTITY_NOT_FOUND
- TRUST_ENTITY_REVOKED
- TRUST_SCORE_LOW_CONFIDENCE
- TRUST_EXCHANGE_APPROVAL_REQUIRED
- VERIFICATION_REQUEST_NOT_FOUND
- COMPLIANCE_PASSPORT_NOT_FOUND
- COMPLIANCE_PASSPORT_SUMMARY_ONLY
- VERIFIABLE_OS_DISABLED
- ATTESTATION_NOT_FOUND
- ATTESTATION_SIGNING_NOT_CONFIGURED
- ATTESTATION_VERIFICATION_FAILED
- EVIDENCE_BUNDLE_NOT_FOUND
- EVIDENCE_BUNDLE_DLP_BLOCKED
- PROVENANCE_LEDGER_INVALID
- AUDIT_EXPORT_BLOCKED
- AI_PROVENANCE_DISABLED
- PROMPT_PROVENANCE_NOT_FOUND
- MODEL_PROVENANCE_NOT_FOUND
- EVAL_PROVENANCE_NOT_FOUND
- DECISION_PROVENANCE_NOT_FOUND
- AI_LINEAGE_INCOMPLETE
- TENANT_ACCESS_DENIED

